PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT * WHERE {
  ?episode fb:tv.tv_episode.characters fb:m.093xn8 .
  ?episode fb:tv.tv_episode.episode_number ?episodeNumber .
  ?episode fb:tv.tv_episode.part_of_season ?season .
  ?season fb:tv.tv_season.season_number ?seasonNumber .
  ?search ?p ?o
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?championship ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.0jnq8 fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:sports.sports_league_championship_event.year ?year
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?year )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?position WHERE {
  fb:m.01jz6d rdfs:comment ?description .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( ?description , 'small forward' ) || CONTAINS( ?description , 'power forward' ) ) .
  BIND( IF( CONTAINS( ?description , 'small forward' ) , 'small forward' , '' ) AS ?sf ) .
  BIND( IF( CONTAINS( ?description , 'power forward' ) , 'power forward' , '' ) AS ?pf ) .
  BIND( CONCAT ( ?sf , IF( ?sf != '' && ?pf != '' , ', ' , '' ) , ?pf ) AS ?position )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  fb:m.01s3vk fb:film.film.starring ?performance .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?actor fb:type.object.name ?actorName .
  FILTER ( ?actorName = 'Johnny Depp' )
}
